<p style="text-align: justify;">Malcom is a Brazilian forward who is meant to replace another Brazilian at Liverpool due to his creativity and goal scoring capacity.</p>
<strong>4. Nabil Fekir</strong>

<img class="aligncenter wp-image-429" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/7-3-300x160.jpg" alt="" width="545" height="291" />

